<L>__{exterior the ambush night (rain)}
<A>__{night is coming down. the tone of the jungle sounds has subtly shifted mellower, more sinuous and certainly scarier. the file stops. king, an experienced point man, listens. chris carrying tex's linked ammo looks around, tense. behind him is gardner, trying to smile, starts to whisper something ('hey taylor ...') when he's abruptly shushed. the file moves on. gardner's pack rattling a little too loud. a weird rush of cold wind now rattles the trees and the monsoon comes. a hard slanting rain, sudden, tropic.}
